This agreement contemplates a professional consulting relationship between Pathfinder
I MPI Consulting and Advanced Pierre Foods' with respect to the opportunities and
projects assigned to Pathfinder I MPI Consulting during the term of this Agreement. As
part of this Agreement, the client assumes full responsibility for any action taken on
recommendations developed by Pathfinder I MPI Consulting if such programs are
implemented by the client, or under the client's direction, and are not implemented
solely by Pathfinder I MPI Consulting.
All rights are reserved and no part may be reproduced, adapted, transmitted or stored in
any retrieval system in any form or medium whether whole or in part without the express
written consent of Pathfinder I MPI Consulting.
In order to reach meaningful conclusions and make actionable recommendations, it will
be necessary for Pathfinder I MPI Consulting to have access to confidential information.
Pathfinder I MPI Consulting commits itself to protect the interests of its clients by
ensuring that confidential information is carefully safeguarded and not revealed to
anyone other than to those people involved in the preparation of the study.
Once the agreement has been signed, Advanced Pierre Foods' will be liable for 50% of
the proposed consulting fees on agreement. If cancellation occurs midway through the
project, other than for Pathfinder I MPI performance, Advanced Pierre Foods' will
liable for an additional 50% of the remaining contract.
